  },
  {
    question: "How long does male face waxing last?",
    answer: "Male face waxing typically lasts 2-4 weeks. Facial hair grows faster than body hair, so more frequent maintenance is needed for the face."
  },
  {
    question: "Will face waxing make my hair grow back thicker?",
    answer: "No, this is a myth. Waxing does not change the structure of your hair follicles. Over time, regular waxing can actually lead to finer, sparser regrowth."
  }
